      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-ide-pgc-azi        to   r-env-cod-azi          .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Codice terminale                    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-ide-pgc-ter        to   r-env-cod-ter          .
