      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-stp-cor-doc-wln      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Linee per trattini                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           add       2                    to   w-stp-cor-doc-wln      .
