           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      15                   to   p-car                  .
           move      w-lpp-iva-ese-lin
                    (w-stp-pie-ctr)       to   p-lin                  .
           move      w-lpp-iva-ese-pos
                    (w-stp-pie-ctr)       to   p-pos                  .
           move      rf-zci-des-doc       to   p-alf                  .
