      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Correzione posizionamento orizzontali in base   *
      *              * all'ampiezza caratteri prescelta                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se correzione da effettuare            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se l'ampiezza caratteri selezionata e'  *
      *                      * a zero, vuol dire che e' stata selezio- *
      *                      * nata una stampante PostScript o HP-GL,  *
      *                      * quindi non si effettuano correzioni     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        p-sel-amc-sel        =    zero
                     go to det-pos-stp-lit-400.
           if      ((w-prs-stf-tmd        =    01  or
                     w-prs-stf-tmd        =    02   ) and
                    (p-sel-amc-sel        =    12,00)   ) or
                   ((w-prs-stf-tmd        =    51  or
                     w-prs-stf-tmd        =    52   ) and
                    (p-sel-amc-sel        =    15,00)   )
                     go to det-pos-stp-lit-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione coefficiente di correzione   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Deviazione in funzione del tipo modulo  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-stf-tmd        =    01 or
                     w-prs-stf-tmd        =    02
                     go to det-pos-stp-lit-310
           else if   w-prs-stf-tmd        =    51 or
                     w-prs-stf-tmd        =    52
                     go to det-pos-stp-lit-320.
       det-pos-stp-lit-310.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo modulo : Senza codice prodotto     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           divide    12                   into p-sel-amc-sel
                                        giving w-det-pos-stp-coe      .
           go to     det-pos-stp-lit-330.
       det-pos-stp-lit-320.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo modulo : Con codice prodotto       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           divide    15                   into p-sel-amc-sel
                                        giving w-det-pos-stp-coe      .
           go to     det-pos-stp-lit-330.
       det-pos-stp-lit-330.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione contatore                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-pmt-fat-ctr          .
       det-pos-stp-lit-332.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento contatore                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-pmt-fat-ctr          .
           if        w-pmt-fat-ctr        >    w-pmt-fat-max
                     go to det-pos-stp-lit-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Calcolo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           multiply  w-det-pos-stp-coe    by   w-lpi-tbl-ele-pos
                                              (w-pmt-fat-ctr)         .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-pos-stp-lit-332.           
       det-pos-stp-lit-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Correzione posizionamenti con displacement o-   *
      *              * rizzontale e verticale                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione contatore                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-pmt-fat-ctr          .
       det-pos-stp-lit-420.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento contatore                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-pmt-fat-ctr          .
           if        w-pmt-fat-ctr        >    w-pmt-fat-max
                     go to det-pos-stp-lit-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Calcolo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       w-dsp-dsp-vrt        to   w-lpi-tbl-ele-lin
                                              (w-pmt-fat-ctr)         .
           add       w-dsp-dsp-hor        to   w-lpi-tbl-ele-pos
                                              (w-pmt-fat-ctr)         .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-pos-stp-lit-420.           
       det-pos-stp-lit-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-pos-stp-lit-999.
       det-pos-stp-lit-999.
           exit.

